						<summary>

						<p>On a rock near the Jaina images on the hill.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription in Vaṭṭeḻuttu characters of c. 10th century records that five images were caused to be made by different persons like a lady disciple and others (whose names are not clear) in the name of certain persons (name lost).</p>						

